{
  "$defs": {
    "BondConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for bond market conventions (e.g., \"USD-UST\", \"USD-CORP\").",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "CapFloorConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for cap/floor market conventions (e.g., \"USD-SOFR-CAP\").",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "CdsConventionKey": {
      "description": "Key to look up CDS conventions (Currency + DocClause).\n\nCDS conventions are identified by both currency and documentation clause, as different\nclauses have different market conventions. Used to look up [`CdsConventions`](crate::market::conventions::defs::CdsConventions)\nfrom the convention registry.\n\n# Examples\n\n```rust\nuse finstack_quant_valuations::market::conventions::ids::{CdsConventionKey, CdsDocClause};\nuse finstack_quant_core::currency::Currency;\n\nlet key = CdsConventionKey {\n    currency: Currency::USD,\n    doc_clause: CdsDocClause::Cr14,\n};\n```",
      "properties": {
        "currency": {
          "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/currency.schema.json",
          "description": "The currency of the CDS."
        },
        "doc_clause": {
          "$ref": "#/$defs/CdsDocClause",
          "description": "The documentation clause (e.g. CR14, MM14)."
        }
      },
      "required": [
        "currency",
        "doc_clause"
      ],
      "type": "object"
    },
    "CdsDocClause": {
      "description": "CDS market standard documentation clauses.\n\nRepresents the ISDA documentation clause used for CDS contracts. Different clauses\ndefine different restructuring events and settlement procedures. Used as part of\n[`CdsConventionKey`] to look up CDS conventions.\n\n# Examples\n\n```rust\nuse finstack_quant_valuations::market::conventions::ids::CdsDocClause;\n\nlet clause = CdsDocClause::Cr14; // Cum-Restructuring 2014\n```",
      "oneOf": [
        {
          "const": "cr14",
          "description": "Cum-Restructuring 2014 (CR14)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "mr14",
          "description": "Modified-Restructuring 2014 (MR14)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "mm14",
          "description": "Modified-Modified-Restructuring 2014 (MM14)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "xr14",
          "description": "No-Restructuring 2014 (XR14)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "isda_na",
          "description": "ISDA North American Corporate (IsdaNa)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "isda_eu",
          "description": "ISDA European Corporate (IsdaEu)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "isda_as",
          "description": "ISDA Asia Corporate (IsdaAs)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "isda_au",
          "description": "ISDA Australia Corporate (IsdaAu)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "isda_nz",
          "description": "ISDA New Zealand Corporate (IsdaNz)",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "custom",
          "description": "Custom / Other",
          "type": "string"
        }
      ]
    },
    "FxConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for FX pair market conventions (e.g., \"EUR/USD\", \"USD/CAD\").",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "FxOptionConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for FX option market conventions (e.g., \"EUR/USD-VANILLA\").",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "InflationSwapConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for Inflation Swap market conventions (e.g., \"USD-CPI\", \"UK-RPI\").\n\nUsed to look up [`InflationSwapConventions`](crate::market::conventions::defs::InflationSwapConventions)\nfrom the convention registry.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "IrFutureContractId": {
      "description": "Stable identifier for an Interest Rate Future contract (e.g., \"CME:SR3\").\n\nUsed to look up [`IrFutureConventions`](crate::market::conventions::defs::IrFutureConventions)\nfrom the convention registry.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "OptionConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for Option market conventions (Equity/FX/Commodity).\n\nUsed to look up [`OptionConventions`](crate::market::conventions::defs::OptionConventions)\nfrom the convention registry.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "OptionType": {
      "description": "Option type for pricing",
      "oneOf": [
        {
          "const": "call",
          "description": "Call option",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "const": "put",
          "description": "Put option",
          "type": "string"
        }
      ]
    },
    "Pillar": {
      "description": "The maturity pillar of a quote.\n\nThe pillar represents the maturity of the instrument referenced by the quote. OTC instruments\n(swaps, deposits) typically use `Tenor` (e.g., \"5Y\") to allow rolling headers that automatically\nadjust as the valuation date changes. Futures or bespoke runs may use `Date` to pin a specific\nmaturity date.\n\n# Examples\n\nUsing a tenor pillar:\n```rust\nuse finstack_quant_valuations::market::quotes::ids::Pillar;\n\n# fn example() -> finstack_quant_core::Result<()> {\nlet pillar = Pillar::Tenor(\"5Y\".parse()?);\n# Ok(())\n# }\n```\n\nUsing a date pillar:\n```rust\nuse finstack_quant_valuations::market::quotes::ids::Pillar;\nuse finstack_quant_core::dates::Date;\n\nlet pillar = Pillar::Date(Date::from_calendar_date(2029, time::Month::June, 20).unwrap());\n```",
      "oneOf": [
        {
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "description": "A relative tenor (e.g., 5Y, 3M).\n\nThe maturity is calculated relative to the valuation date, allowing quotes to \"roll\"\nforward automatically. This is the standard approach for OTC instruments.",
          "properties": {
            "tenor": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/tenor.schema.json"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "tenor"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "description": "An absolute date.\n\nThe maturity is fixed to a specific date, regardless of the valuation date. This is\ntypically used for futures contracts or bespoke instruments with fixed maturities.",
          "properties": {
            "date": {
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "date"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        }
      ]
    },
    "QuoteId": {
      "description": "A stable identifier for a market quote (e.g., \"USD-OIS-SWAP-5Y\").\n\nThis ID is used for human readability, logging, and potentially matching against external\ndata sources. Quote IDs should be unique within a calibration set and follow a consistent\nnaming convention (e.g., \"{currency}-{index}-{type}-{pillar}\").\n\n# Examples\n\n```rust\nuse finstack_quant_valuations::market::quotes::ids::QuoteId;\n\nlet id = QuoteId::new(\"USD-SOFR-DEP-1M\");\nassert_eq!(id.as_str(), \"USD-SOFR-DEP-1M\");\n```",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "SwaptionConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for Swaption market conventions (e.g., \"USD\", \"EUR\").\n\nUsed to look up [`SwaptionConventions`](crate::market::conventions::defs::SwaptionConventions)\nfrom the convention registry.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "XccyConventionId": {
      "description": "Identifier for cross-currency swap market conventions (e.g., \"EUR/USD-XCCY\").",
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "$id": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/market/1/market_quote.schema.json",
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "description": "Tagged union of all supported market quote types (rates, CDS, FX, vol, inflation, etc.)",
  "oneOf": [
    {
      "description": "Bond instruments",
      "oneOf": [
        {
          "description": "Fixed-rate bullet bond quoted in clean price (% of par).",
          "properties": {
            "clean_price_pct": {
              "description": "Quoted clean price as percent of par.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "convention": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/BondConventionId",
              "description": "Bond convention identifier."
            },
            "coupon_rate": {
              "description": "Annual coupon rate in decimal form.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "currency": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/currency.schema.json",
              "description": "Settlement / pricing currency of the bond."
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "issue_date": {
              "description": "Bond issue date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "maturity": {
              "description": "Bond maturity date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "fixed_rate_bullet_clean_price",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "currency",
            "issue_date",
            "maturity",
            "coupon_rate",
            "convention",
            "clean_price_pct"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "description": "Fixed-rate bullet bond quoted in Z-spread over a discount curve (decimal).",
          "properties": {
            "convention": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/BondConventionId",
              "description": "Bond convention identifier."
            },
            "coupon_rate": {
              "description": "Annual coupon rate in decimal form.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "currency": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/currency.schema.json",
              "description": "Settlement / pricing currency of the bond."
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "issue_date": {
              "description": "Bond issue date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "maturity": {
              "description": "Bond maturity date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "fixed_rate_bullet_z_spread",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "z_spread": {
              "description": "Z-spread in decimal form (e.g. 0.01 = 100bp).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "currency",
            "issue_date",
            "maturity",
            "coupon_rate",
            "convention",
            "z_spread"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "description": "Fixed-rate bullet bond quoted in OAS (decimal).",
          "properties": {
            "convention": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/BondConventionId",
              "description": "Bond convention identifier."
            },
            "coupon_rate": {
              "description": "Annual coupon rate in decimal form.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "currency": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/currency.schema.json",
              "description": "Settlement / pricing currency of the bond."
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "issue_date": {
              "description": "Bond issue date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "maturity": {
              "description": "Bond maturity date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "oas": {
              "description": "Option-adjusted spread in decimal form (e.g. 0.005 = 50bp).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "fixed_rate_bullet_oas",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "currency",
            "issue_date",
            "maturity",
            "coupon_rate",
            "convention",
            "oas"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "description": "Fixed-rate bullet bond quoted in yield-to-maturity (decimal).",
          "properties": {
            "convention": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/BondConventionId",
              "description": "Bond convention identifier."
            },
            "coupon_rate": {
              "description": "Annual coupon rate in decimal form.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "currency": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/currency.schema.json",
              "description": "Settlement / pricing currency of the bond."
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "issue_date": {
              "description": "Bond issue date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "maturity": {
              "description": "Bond maturity date.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "fixed_rate_bullet_ytm",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "ytm": {
              "description": "Yield to maturity in decimal form.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "currency",
            "issue_date",
            "maturity",
            "coupon_rate",
            "convention",
            "ytm"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "class": {
          "const": "bond",
          "type": "string"
        }
      },
      "required": [
        "class"
      ],
      "type": "object"
    },
    {
      "description": "Interest rate instruments",
      "oneOf": [
        {
          "description": "Money market deposit rate.",
          "properties": {
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "index": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/id.schema.json",
              "description": "Rate index identifier (e.g. \"USD-SOFR-3M\")."
            },
            "pillar": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/Pillar",
              "description": "Maturity pillar (e.g. Tenor(\"3M\") or Date(\"2024-01-01\"))."
            },
            "rate": {
              "description": "Rate value (decimal).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "deposit",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "index",
            "pillar",
            "rate"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "description": "Forward Rate Agreement.",
          "properties": {
            "end": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/Pillar",
              "description": "End date pillar."
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "index": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/id.schema.json",
              "description": "Rate index identifier."
            },
            "rate": {
              "description": "Rate value (decimal).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "start": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/Pillar",
              "description": "Start date pillar."
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "fra",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "index",
            "start",
            "end",
            "rate"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "description": "Interest Rate Future (price).",
          "properties": {
            "contract": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/IrFutureContractId",
              "description": "Future contract identifier (e.g. \"CME:SR3\")."
            },
            "convexity_adjustment": {
              "default": null,
              "description": "Optional convexity adjustment (rate, decimal).\n\nThis fixed value is currently required for calibration. If omitted,\nfutures-quote calibration will fail closed rather than silently assume\nzero or attempt an unwired dynamic lookup.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": [
                "number",
                "null"
              ]
            },
            "expiry": {
              "description": "Expiry date of the future.",
              "format": "date",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "price": {
              "description": "Price of the future (e.g. 98.50).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "futures",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "vol_surface_id": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/id.schema.json"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "default": null,
              "description": "Optional volatility surface identifier for dynamic convexity adjustment.\n\nReserved for future dynamic convexity support. Until that wiring exists,\nproviding `vol_surface_id` without `convexity_adjustment` is treated as\nan invalid quote shape during calibration."
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "contract",
            "expiry",
            "price"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "description": "Interest Rate Swap (par rate).",
          "properties": {
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "index": {
              "$ref": "https://finstack_quant.dev/schemas/common/1/id.schema.json",
              "description": "Rate index identifier (floating leg)."
            },
            "pillar": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/Pillar",
              "description": "Maturity pillar of the swap."
            },
            "rate": {
              "description": "Fixed rate (decimal) making the swap PV=0.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "spread_decimal": {
              "default": null,
              "description": "Optional spread over the index in decimal format (e.g., 0.0010 for 10 basis points).\n\nThis spread is added to the floating leg rate. The value is in decimal format\nand will be converted to basis points internally (multiplied by 10,000).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": [
                "number",
                "null"
              ]
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "swap",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "index",
            "pillar",
            "rate"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "class": {
          "const": "rates",
          "type": "string"
        }
      },
      "required": [
        "class"
      ],
      "type": "object"
    },
    {
      "description": "Credit default swaps",
      "oneOf": [
        {
          "description": "Credit Default Swap (par spread).",
          "properties": {
            "convention": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/CdsConventionKey",
              "description": "Convention key (currency + doc clause)."
            },
            "entity": {
              "description": "Reference entity name.",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "pillar": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/Pillar",
              "description": "Maturity pillar."
            },
            "recovery_rate": {
              "description": "Recovery rate assumption (e.g. 0.40).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "spread_bp": {
              "description": "Par spread in basis points (e.g. 100.0).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "cds_par_spread",
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "entity",
            "convention",
            "pillar",
            "spread_bp",
            "recovery_rate"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "description": "Credit Default Swap (upfront + running).",
          "properties": {
            "convention": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/CdsConventionKey",
              "description": "Convention key."
            },
            "entity": {
              "description": "Reference entity name.",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "id": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/QuoteId",
              "description": "Unique identifier for the quote."
            },
            "pillar": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/Pillar",
              "description": "Maturity pillar."
            },
            "recovery_rate": {
              "description": "Recovery rate assumption.",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "running_spread_bp": {
              "description": "Running spread in basis points (e.g. 100.0 or 500.0).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            },
            "type": {
              "const": "cds_upfront",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "upfront_pct": {
              "description": "Upfront payment percentage of notional (e.g. 0.01 for 1%).",
              "format": "double",
              "type": "number"
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "type",
            "id",
            "entity",
            "convention",
            "pillar",
            "running_spread_bp",
            "upfront_pct",
            "recovery_rate"
          ],
          "type": "object"
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "class": {
          "const": "cds",
          "type": "string"
        }
      },
      "required": [
